Melinda Gates Just Threw Her Daughter, Jennifer, a Wedding ShowerJennifer Gates, a professional show jumper—and the daughter of Melinda Gates—is engaged to her longtime boyfriend Nayel Nassar, a fellow equestrian who represented Egypt in this summer's Tokyo Olympics.

In January 2020, Gates shared the news on Instagram, with photo of the two of them in the snow—and Jennifer, looking shocked, sporting her new ring. "Nayel Nassar, you are one of a kind," she wrote. "Absolutely swept me off my feet this past weekend, surprising me in the most meaningful location over one of our many shared passions. I can’t wait to spend the rest of our lives learning, growing, laughing and loving together. Yes a million times over
